## Summary
This documentation page explains Amplitude's Persona Charts feature, which uses cluster analysis to group users based on similar event behaviors, helping product teams discover user personas without predefined rules. The page details how to set up persona charts, interpret cluster cards, and identify meaningful user personas through the event table visualization.

